{"sections":{"567fa266-e3a3-4d42-8bd7-d5c0c15798dd":{"type":"image-with-text-overlay","blocks":{"template--14745674219578__567fa266-e3a3-4d42-8bd7-d5c0c15798dd-heading-1":{"type":"heading","settings":{"text":"","heading_size":"h1-xlarge"}}},"block_order":["template--14745674219578__567fa266-e3a3-4d42-8bd7-d5c0c15798dd-heading-1"],"custom_css":[],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/DSCF2621_medium_11730a75-7cd2-417f-a1bf-cf7459663ada.jpg","mobile_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/DSCF2621_medium_11730a75-7cd2-417f-a1bf-cf7459663ada.jpg","image_parallax":true,"desktop_height":"desktop-height-450","mobile_height":"mobile-height-350","image_focal_point_y":50,"mob_image_focal_point_y":50,"enable_focal_control":false,"full_width":true,"content_width":"medium","content_position":"middle-center","text_alignment":"center","text_color":"#ffffff","overlay_color":"#35393d","overlay_opacity":9,"disable_top_spacing":true,"disable_bottom_spacing":true}},"rich_text_GFVwhC":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"heading_mfCkw6":{"type":"heading","settings":{"text":"Edisto Fleece: Lived in Vibes, Right Out of the Box","marker_style":"style1","size":"h3","marker_color":"#fd6262"}},"text_w8UnhU":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>We kicked off the year with a road trip down to Edisto Island, SC to capture the inspiration of our newest collection. For visitors and locals alike, this place creates a feeling you'll carry with you anywhere. A community built by the water, for the water. A place to go in your mind where it all makes sense - heritage, simplicity, and a water first way of life.<\/p><p>The new Edisto Collection is as timeless as its namesake. Crafted from soft, durable French terry, it delivers easy warmth and everyday comfort - shaped by salt air, shifting tides, and a way of life that hasn’t changed in generations. <\/p>","size":"text-size-large"}}},"block_order":["heading_mfCkw6","text_w8UnhU"],"custom_css":["{background-color: #f7f4ef;}","p {color: black;}",".button {margin-top: 10px;}"],"settings":{"id":"","text_width":"xlarge","text_position":"center","text_alignment":"center","color_bg":"#f7f4ef","color_heading":"#0E4175","color_text":"#0581ff","color_links":"#0581ff","full_bleed_layout":true,"disable_top_spacing":true,"disable_bottom_spacing":true}},"featured_collection_fjGC6f":{"type":"featured-collection","name":"Featured collection","settings":{"heading":"TERRY FLEECE YOU'LL LIVE IN","marker_style":"style1","description":"<p>Easy layers, premium French terry, and everyday comfort - shop the fleece you’ll wear on repeat.<\/p>","collection":"edisto-collection","display_type":"carousel","product_limit":7,"columns_desktop":4,"show_view_all":true,"mobile_swipe":true,"show_progress_bar":true,"marker_color":"#fd6262","disable_top_spacing":true,"disable_bottom_spacing":false}},"video_mnpttM":{"type":"video","settings":{"heading":"","marker_style":"style1","description":"","full_width":false,"video":"","video_hosted":"shopify:\/\/files\/videos\/Reduced Edisto Night.mov","video_autoplay":true,"aspect_ratio":"16-9","marker_color":"#fd6262","disable_top_spacing":true,"disable_bottom_spacing":false}},"image_with_text_EiGFtq":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"heading_cjPrfx":{"type":"heading","settings":{"text":"ROOTED IN TRADITION","marker_style":"style1","heading_size":"h3","marker_color":"#fd6262"}},"text_gr8Cw7":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Our most versatile fleece program, the Edisto is designed for comfort that lasts all year. Easy warmth for cool summer mornings, an extra layer when the breeze rolls in, and the piece you reach for when the fire’s going and the day slows down. Thoughtfully designed with clean lines and lived-in comfort, Edisto is built for a simpler way of life - where the only soundtrack is the water, wind, and the rhythm of the coast.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["heading_cjPrfx","text_gr8Cw7"],"name":"Image with text","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Huk_CrystalRiver_04440_medium_7314358d-3fff-4054-b519-bac23e09c884.jpg","use_video":false,"video":"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=_9VUPq3SxOc","video_autoplay":false,"height":"adapt","desktop_image_width":"medium","full_width":true,"layout":"text_first","content_position":"text-left","column_spacing":"small","color_bg":"#ffffff","color_text":"#2c2d2e","color_border":"#e2e2e2","disable_top_spacing":true,"disable_bottom_spacing":true}},"image_with_text_ryVUQG":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"heading_kcfcUp":{"type":"heading","settings":{"text":"the edisto difference","marker_style":"style1","heading_size":"h3","marker_color":"#FD6262"}},"text_yEF6Gf":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Our exclusive French terry is designed to deliver comfort without compromise. Soft and breathable with just enough warmth to take the chill off, it’s made to wear easily across seasons. Durable, versatile, and comfortable on its own or layered, this is a true 12-month fleece built to move with you and feel better the more wears it gets.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["heading_kcfcUp","text_yEF6Gf"],"name":"Image with text","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/DSCF2547-2_medium_9770ae02-7638-4f8c-939b-ffdd64ade8e4.jpg","use_video":false,"video":"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=_9VUPq3SxOc","video_autoplay":true,"height":"adapt","desktop_image_width":"medium","full_width":false,"layout":"image_first","content_position":"text-left","column_spacing":"small","color_bg":"#ffffff","color_text":"#2c2d2e","color_border":"#e2e2e2","disable_top_spacing":true,"disable_bottom_spacing":true}},"image_with_text_overlay_6UzWMi":{"type":"image-with-text-overlay","blocks":{"heading_zkmWWC":{"type":"heading","settings":{"text":"MARSH GRASS CAMO","heading_size":"h1-xlarge"}},"text_gNhG44":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Inspired by the seagrasses that shape the Lowcountry, this custom camo reflects the layered textures, muted tones, and natural movement of the coast. Designed to blend into the landscape, it captures the quiet beauty of a place where land and water meet.<\/p>","description_size":"medium"}}},"block_order":["heading_zkmWWC","text_gNhG44"],"name":"Image with text overlay","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Seagrass_Marsh_Camo_Pattern.jpg","image_parallax":false,"desktop_height":"desktop-height-450","mobile_height":"mobile-height-500","image_focal_point_y":50,"mob_image_focal_point_y":50,"enable_focal_control":false,"full_width":true,"content_width":"large","content_position":"middle-center","text_alignment":"center","text_color":"#14281a","overlay_color":"#9fa3a7","overlay_opacity":8,"disable_top_spacing":true,"disable_bottom_spacing":true}},"collection_tabs_xeNMgg":{"type":"collection-tabs","blocks":{"collection_za9Cjb":{"type":"collection","settings":{"collection":"airweight-collection","show_alternate_images":false,"enable_promotion":true,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Airweight-Landing-Collection.jpg","title":"","text":"","link_label":"SHOP NOW","content_position":"bottom-center","text_alignment":"center","link":"shopify:\/\/collections\/airweight-collection","use_text_button":false,"block_link":"shopify:\/\/collections\/airweight-collection","overlay_color":"#000000","overlay_opacity":12}}},"block_order":["collection_za9Cjb"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"heading":"Shop the Collection","marker_style":"style1","description":"","product_limit":16,"columns_desktop":4,"show_progress_bar":false,"marker_color":"#ffffff","bg-color":"#ffffff","disable_top_spacing":false,"disable_bottom_spacing":false}},"8ab8f1f0-7339-452e-9f95-73816fef5c9e":{"type":"testimonials","blocks":{"template--14745674219578__8ab8f1f0-7339-452e-9f95-73816fef5c9e-quote-3":{"type":"quote","settings":{"stars":"","text":"\"The new Icon shirt is Huk's best shirt yet.  Being a south Florida Captain the heat is what will keep you from wanting to go out. The I.C.E. tech is legit.  You can feel it cooling your skin allowing me to stay comfortable all day on the water.\"","author":"Thomas L."}},"quote_bUj6VJ":{"type":"quote","settings":{"stars":"","text":"\"Great fitting shirt! The hood is big enough to cover the sides of your face. Very cool even in 95 degrees. Light and comfortable material, with great sun protection.\"","author":"Tod H."}},"template--14745674219578__8ab8f1f0-7339-452e-9f95-73816fef5c9e-quote-1":{"type":"quote","settings":{"stars":"","text":"\"I had a great experience! It's always a good feeling when a product lives up to its description. Staying comfortable and protected from the elements is key for any successful fishing trip. A good hoodie can make all the difference when you're out on the water. It sounds like I found a winner wearing the HUK Icon hoodie.\"","author":"Bebee M."}},"template--14745674219578__8ab8f1f0-7339-452e-9f95-73816fef5c9e-quote-2":{"type":"quote","settings":{"stars":"","text":"\"The Huk Icon Performance Hoodie is as essential as the hook on the end of your line. Plain and simple, get it.\"","author":"Shane E."}}},"block_order":["template--14745674219578__8ab8f1f0-7339-452e-9f95-73816fef5c9e-quote-3","quote_bUj6VJ","template--14745674219578__8ab8f1f0-7339-452e-9f95-73816fef5c9e-quote-1","template--14745674219578__8ab8f1f0-7339-452e-9f95-73816fef5c9e-quote-2"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"heading":"TESTIMONIALS","full_width":true,"text_size":"medium","font_family":"body","pagination":"dots","autoplay":true,"autoplay_length":5,"color_bg":"#f7f4ef","color_text":"#0581ff","disable_top_spacing":false,"disable_bottom_spacing":false}},"scrolling_images_m3DYFP":{"type":"scrolling-images","blocks":{"image_y4TGrf":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Edisto-Scroll-7.jpg","link":"","heading":"","text":""}},"image_gtQkqb":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Edisto-Scroll-1.jpg","link":"","heading":"","text":""}},"image_7c6Ltj":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Edisto-Scroll-2.jpg","link":"","heading":"","text":""}},"image_BLTFrn":{"type":"image","setti